{"id":2991,"date":"2024-08-20T14:55:25","date_gmt":"2024-08-20T07:55:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2991"},"modified":"2024-08-20T14:55:25","modified_gmt":"2024-08-20T07:55:25","slug":"cac-buoc-nhap-hoc-truc-tuyen-tai-truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/cac-buoc-nhap-hoc-truc-tuyen-tai-truong-dai-hoc-thanh-do\/","title":{"rendered":"C\u00c1C B\u01af\u1edaC NH\u1eacP H\u1eccC TR\u1ef0C TUY\u1ebeN T\u1ea0I TR\u01af\u1edcNG \u0110\u1ea0I H\u1eccC TH\u00c0NH \u0110\u00d4"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Sau khi x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean c\u1ed5ng th\u00f4ng tin chung, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n t\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1eadc ph\u1ee5 huynh \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc d\u01b0\u1edbi <b>02 <\/b>h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c <strong>tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp <\/strong>ho\u1eb7c<strong> tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn.<\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<p>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn <strong>h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn<\/strong> th\u00ec d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc chi ti\u1ebft. B\u1ea1n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t theo c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 nha.<\/p>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/SKrWiQ3Y0yo?si=mF4Ho6TRi74sbwef\" width=\"560\" height=\"314\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><\/iframe><\/p>\n<h3><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1 &#8211; \u0110\u0103ng nh\u1eadp<\/b><\/h3>\n<h3>Th\u00ed sinh truy c\u1eadp v\u00e0o website: <a href=\"http:\/\/sv.thanhdo.edu.vn\/nhap-hoc-truc-tuyen.html\"><strong>Nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn<\/strong><\/a> ho\u1eb7c qu\u00e9t <strong>m\u00e3 QR<\/strong> d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<\/h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-22893\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Screenshot-2024-08-17-at-4.35.06%E2%80%AFPM.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"145\" height=\"174\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: Tra c\u1ee9u<\/b> th\u00ed sinh: Th\u00ed sinh nh\u1eadp c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin: M\u00e3 h\u1ed3 s\u01a1, S\u0110T, M\u00e3 x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u1ea5n n\u00fat <strong>TRA C\u1ee8U.<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li><i>L\u01b0u \u00fd: Th\u00ed sinh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00fang m\u00e3 nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qua tin nh\u1eafn SMS ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u00ean gi\u1ea5y b\u00e1o nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc <\/i>(VD: 223TDD101A.0001).<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17462\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ThanhtoanTT1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"694\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3 &#8211; Ki\u1ec3m tra<\/b> ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin th\u00ed sinh, th\u00f4ng tin tr\u00fang tuy\u1ec3n sau \u0111\u00f3 \u1ea5n n\u00fat <strong>TI\u1ebeP T\u1ee4C.<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17464\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ThanhtoanTT2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"722\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 4 &#8211; Th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean l\u1ea1c<\/b>: \u0110i\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean h\u1ec7 bao g\u1ed3m: S\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, Email, \u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9, Ghi ch\u00fa r\u1ed3i b\u1ea5m <strong>TI\u1ebeP T\u1ee4C.<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-17466\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/ThanhtoanTT3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"782\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 5 &#8211; Thanh to\u00e1n<\/b><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Ch\u1ecdn h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c<strong> Thanh to\u00e1n tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn:<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Ch\u1ecdn <strong>Baokim<\/strong> sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ecdn <strong>THANH TO\u00c1N V\u1edaI QR CODE <\/strong>\u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u00e0 l\u00e0m theo h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp theo tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-17847\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Thanhtoan5.1-1024x538.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"538\" \/><\/p>\n<p>M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u00e3 QR, b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n thanh to\u00e1n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c qu\u00e9t QR code ho\u1eb7c t\u1ea3i \u1ea3nh QR code v\u1ec1 m\u00e1y v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00e0nh to\u00e1n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u00ean t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-17849\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Thanhtoan5.2-1024x534.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" \/>Sau khi H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng x\u1eed l\u00fd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thanh to\u00e1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. B\u1ea1n ch\u1ee5p l\u1ea1i m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea7n thanh to\u00e1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<br \/>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-17851\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/Thanhtoan5.3-1024x588.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"588\" \/><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ch\u1ecdn h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c<strong> Chuy\u1ec3n kho\u1ea3n:<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-17470 alignleft\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/QR-Thanhtoan.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"157\" height=\"203\" \/><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n kho\u1ea3n<\/strong><br \/>\n\u2022 T\u00ean t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n: <strong>Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Tha\u0300nh \u0110\u00f4<\/strong><br \/>\n\u2022 S\u00f4\u0301 ta\u0300i khoa\u0309n: <strong>113000146722<\/strong><br \/>\n\u2022 Ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng <strong>TMCP C\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (Vietinbank)<\/strong> &#8211; chi nh\u00e1nh Nam Th\u0103ng Long &#8211; H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<br \/>\n\u2022 N\u1ed9i dung chuy\u1ec3n kho\u1ea3n: <strong>H\u1ecd v\u00e0 t\u00ean_ Ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng n\u0103m sinh_Ng\u00e0nh h\u1ecdc<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>&gt;&gt; Th\u00ed sinh qu\u00e9t m\u00e3 QR \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh thanh to\u00e1n:<\/p>\n<p>&gt;&gt; Khi m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh b\u00e1o thanh to\u00e1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. \u1ea4n n\u00fat Chuy\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 trang tr\u01b0\u1edbc ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ee3i 7s \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 trang tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 6 &#8211; K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-17458\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/3-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" \/><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Th\u00ed sinh ki\u1ec3m tra l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n kho\u1ea3n, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u1ea5n n\u00fat HO\u00c0N TH\u00c0NH \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 B\u01b0\u1edbc 1.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Th\u00ed sinh nh\u1eadp c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin: M\u00e3 h\u1ed3 s\u01a1, S\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, M\u00e3 x\u00e1c th\u1ef1c v\u00e0 \u1ea5n n\u00fat TRA C\u1ee8U \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><b>B\u01b0\u1edbc 7 &#8211; Truy c\u1eadp t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n sinh vi\u00ean<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-17456\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/2-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh b\u01b0\u1edbc 6 sinh vi\u00ean s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c <strong>M\u00e3 sinh vi\u00ean<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>&#8211; Sinh vi\u00ean truy c\u1eadp trang website: <strong><a href=\"http:\/\/sv.thanhdo.edu.vn\/sinh-vien-dang-nhap.html\">http:\/\/sv.thanhdo.edu.vn\/sinh-vien-dang-nhap.html<\/a><\/strong><strong>\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><i>*L\u01b0u \u00fd:\u00a0<\/i><\/p>\n<p><i>&#8211; T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n: <strong>M\u00e3 sinh vi\u00ean<\/strong><\/i><\/p>\n<p><i>&#8211; M\u1eadt kh\u1ea9u ban \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh: <strong>1111<\/strong><\/i><\/p>\n<p>Sau khi thanh to\u00e1n h\u1ecdc ph\u00ed v\u00e0 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh T\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4.<\/p>\n<p>H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 vi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n<blockquote><p>M\u1ecdi th\u00f4ng tin th\u1eafc m\u1eafc vui l\u00f2ng g\u1eedi v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9:<\/p>\n<p><b>V\u0103n ph\u00f2ng Trung t\u00e2m Tuy\u1ec3n sinh<\/b>, T\u1ea7ng 1, Nh\u00e0 A, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9: Km15, Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 32, Kim Chung, Ho\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/p>\n<p>Hotline: 0934 07 8668 \u2013 0243 386 1601<\/p>\n<p>Website: <a href=\"http:\/\/nhaphoc.thanhdo.edu.vn\/\">http:\/\/nhaphoc.thanhdo.edu.vn<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Fanpage: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/truongdaihocthanhdo\">https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/truongdaihocthanhdo<\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Sau khi x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean c\u1ed5ng th\u00f4ng tin chung, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n t\u00e2n sinh vi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1eadc ph\u1ee5 huynh \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadp h\u1ecdc d\u01b0\u1edbi 02 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c tr\u1ef1c [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":2578,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[36,23,1],"tags":[109,110,103,179,42,125],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2991"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2991"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2991\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2992,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2991\/revisions\/2992"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2578"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2991"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2991"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2991"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\